{
  "id": "6a2928f624768267a8532c3e",
  "title": "ランタナさんの写真撮らせ力",
  "created": 1781082359,
  "updated": 1781089381,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a2928f624768267a8532c3e",
      "text": "ランタナさんの写真撮らせ力",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082372
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fc8",
      "text": "from [2026/06/09]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fc9",
      "text": "通りがかった[道端の花][terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082379
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fca",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/c3ea837b655a03112d1b8df81521e08d]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fcb",
      "text": "\t2色あるーと思って撮った",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fcc",
      "text": "\t花の名前は知らない",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fcd",
      "text": "\t [ランタナ]かな？[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fce",
      "text": "\t  自分も昔写真を撮った、名前はその時調べたが忘れててまた調べた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fcf",
      "text": "\t  [2024/10/27]らしい(井戸端ではない)",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd0",
      "text": "\t\t大仏も[2024/10/07]に撮っていた[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd1",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/ce4cead40b4f4394d03bc6a1f0883cd4]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd2",
      "text": "\t\t\tGoogle appでランタナだと調べたスクショも残っていた 笑",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd3",
      "text": "\t\t\t\thttps://gyazo.com/65a4ca4da342f5f264a8c34055efbb35",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a29445a000000000031c7e1",
      "text": "\t\t\t当時通っていた大学の構内に生えてた",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1781089371,
      "updated": 1781089381
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd4",
      "text": "\t\t[知見.icon] [terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd5",
      "text": "\t\tランタナさんの[写真撮らせ力]すごいな[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd6",
      "text": "\t蟻さんが写り込んでいることに今気がついた",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    },
    {
      "id": "6a2928f60000000000572fd7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1781082359,
      "updated": 1781082359
    }
  ]
}